flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Auth{Authenticated?}
  Auth -- No --> Login[ARES Login]
  Login --> Fetch[Fetch Published Survey]
  Auth -- Yes --> Fetch
  Fetch --> Render[Render Visible Root Questions]
  Render --> Answer[User Selects Answer]
  Answer --> Resolve[Run RCLR Recursively]
  Resolve --> Version{Schema Version Changed?}
  Version -- No --> Complete{Visible Required Path Complete?}
  Version -- Yes --> Recover{Can Map Answers?}
  Recover -- Yes --> Atomic[Atomic State Recovery]
  Recover -- No --> Rollback[Rollback To Stable Node]
  Atomic --> Render
  Rollback --> Render
  Complete -- No --> Render
  Complete -- Yes --> Send[Enable Send Button]
  Send --> End([Submitted])
